# Egyptian ID Validator (Python)

[![GitHub tag](https://img.shields.io/github/v/tag/MohamedAAbdallah/Egyptian-ID-Validator-Py?label=latest%20tag)](https://github.com/MohamedAAbdallah/Egyptian-ID-Validator-Py/tags)
